name: Capybara
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Capybara is a Decentralized meme coin on Solana designed to be Community experiment , raising fund to build game “Play for Fun and Fun to Earn". 

CAPY created from Spl-token on Solana  that is used for:

-Participation on community activities 
-Fees for playing game to earn reward
